-----------------------------------------------------------------
                 Connecting to Server 
-----------------------------------------------------------------
            1. Go into Customer_Package "bin" directory 
            2. run command "./ChatGUI"
       ***note: hostname/port no. do not need to be specified;
           however, client cannot run on host zuma.eecs.uci.edu***
------------------------------------------------------------------
                      Logging In
------------------------------------------------------------------
            3. Input username: "USER"
            4. Input password: "213123"
            5. Click "Log In" button
------------------------------------------------------------------
                        Chatting
------------------------------------------------------------------
            10. You can now start chatting with your friend, ADMIN
------------------------------------------------------------------
                        Emojis
------------------------------------------------------------------
            11. Don't forget to fully express yourself with emojis!
------------------------------------------------------------------
                        Exiting
------------------------------------------------------------------
            12. When done chatting, quit by exiting out 
            
            
